AI Office Furniture Mockup Generator

Business Impact
Turnaround Efficiency: Reduced design turnaround time for lifestyle mockups by ~99% (from 2 weeks to <1 minute).

Scalability: Enabled instant visualization for a catalog of 60,000+ SKUs.

The Problem
Ergospace required high-quality lifestyle imagery for its vast marketplace catalog, but manual 3D rendering and Photoshop compositing created a massive operational bottleneck.

The Solution
An internal tool built to empower the design team to generate photorealistic office environments using GenAI.

Frontend: Responsive UI built with Tailwind CSS.

Backend: Firebase for secure team authentication and Firestore for a shared organizational gallery.

Engine: Google Gemini 2.5 Flash Image Preview API for high-fidelity image-to-image generation.

Project Structure
/app: Contains the core application index.html.

/docs: Includes the Product Requirement Document (PRD) and Technical Logic.

/assets: UI components and sample product mockups.
